 />\n新僑係近20年移民果批支那人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T01:08:42.000Z","msg":"都無咩分別 中共咁搞落去最後一定攬炒 好快排華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T01:22:33.000Z","msg":"越南、日本人都慘被牽連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e908ac826bd348a0094137e30077fc38c4bef1a","tid":794382,"uid":6497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T01:27:27.000Z","msg":"份報告唔只講咁少<br />\n仲有點名董伯伯係頭號共諜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d10158599035d2d8ec268553dde0556c6e16689","tid":794382,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T05:11:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ba8ad52f93d8ba5cf02a5794ea24251d72c4258","tid":794382,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e908ac826bd348a0094137e30077fc38c4bef1a","tid":794382,"uid":6497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T01:27:27.000Z","msg":"份報告唔只講咁少<br />\n仲有點名董伯伯係頭號共諜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T05:11:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}